{"name":"Enhanced Creativity","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You are more imaginative and inclined to think outside the\nbox. Apply a +10 modifier to Know or Technical skill tests where creativity plays a major role. This level of ingenuity sometimes seems strange and unusual, manifesting as odd insights or creepy details, especially with artwork.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"0eQGK6udgUJikNRP"}
{"name":"Deja Vu","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your force the target’s mind into recursive loop. They will repeat their actions from the previous 15–30 seconds (5–10 action turns) for the next WIL ÷ 5 minutes. They will repeat their actions as closely as possible, even if their environment and circumstances change. \n\nIf someone actively interrupts or restrains the target, or\notherwise disrupts the loop, they may make a WIL Check to break out of the loop, ending the sleight.","active":true,"infection":8,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"2HPn7jPKSdz7Hnmc"}
{"name":"Mindlink","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You establish two-way mental communication with the target.\nIf mindlinked with more than one target simultaneously, you may act as a telepathic server so that everyone mindlinked with you can also telepathically communicate with each other (though you will overhear everything). Language is still a factor in mindlinked communications, but this barrier may be overcome by transmitting sounds, images, emotions, and other sensations.","active":true,"infection":2,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Quick","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"2JDlIiHDpw7eSE9H"}
{"name":"Predictive Boost","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your brain’s bayesian probability functions are accelerated,\nenhancing your ability to estimate and predict the outcomes of events as they unfold in real-time around you. In effect, you have an intuitive sense for the most likely outcomes. +2 Initiative.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"5Nzq9KD9qzWo5B5X"}
{"name":"Deep Scan","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Deep Scan is a more intrusive version of Browse Thoughts. You telepathically invade the target’s mind and probe it for information. You extract two pieces of information (i.e., a name, image, passcode, description or summary a few sentences long, or a memory of less than a minute) plus two for each superior success.\n\nEach item takes one full action turn to retrieve, during which the sleight must be sustained.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"62CriYlaG0f1UsKx"}
{"name":"Pain","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You activate the target’s nerve endings and clusters, inflicting a painful burning sensation. Treat as a pain effect; the target must take their next action to flee away from the async or area at full movement.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"86xWjYFz7geICg85"}
{"name":"Animal Control","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You take over the mind of a non-sapient animal. While sustained, you control the animal exactly like remotely operating a drone. You may switch between autonomous mode and jamming.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"9wKpI8agA9svkdP6"}
{"name":"Invigorate","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You trigger a rush of neurochemical energy in the target. They may expend their next complex action collecting themselves; this counts as a short recharge action, without needing to expend the full 10 minutes. Note that this sleight does not provide an extra recharge, it simply shortens the time frame.","active":true,"infection":4,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"Bermqa2S1JGwARcK"}
{"name":"Infectious Mind","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You share a triggered disorder or active infection influence effect with the target. At the GM’s discretion, prolonged exposure may inflict stress damage to the target.","active":true,"infection":4,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"CBdZryaHyXrQ8YIy"}
{"name":"Control Behavior","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You can fine-tune your emotional state. Apply an Enhanced\nBehavior or Restricted Behavior (Level 2) trait ▶80 of your\nchoice at will. You may not change it again until you have taken a recharge action. \n\nAt the GM's discretion, this trait may apply a +/–10 modifier in some situations. Alternatively, use this to reduce an Enhanced/Restricted Behavior trait imposed on you by up to two levels. You can push this sleight","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"CNNctOKYaZnVC2ru"}
{"name":"Pattern Recognition","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You are adept at spotting patterns and correlating non-random elements. This is useful for translating languages, breaking codes, or finding clues hidden among massive amounts of data. \n\nApply a +10 modifier to appropriate Infosec, Perceive, or Research Tests where you have a sufficiently large sample and time enough to study, as determined by the gamemaster.\n\nThis might range from a few hours of investigating inscriptions left by long-dead aliens to a week or more of researching a lengthy cipher. This does not apply to bruteforce hacking or Infosec tests made by decrypt apps to break a code.\n\nYou also learn new languages easily; reduce the timeframe to weeks rather than months.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"CTVPCvCNvN0xP0IB"}
{"name":"Social Cunning","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your emotional intelligence is sharpened and focused, making you more manipulative and exploitive of weaknesses. +10 to Persuade and Provoke Tests.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"CyhJv8hoB42IuGz1"}
{"name":"Induce Error","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You create a glitch in the target’s mind that causes them to unconsciously do something wrong. The target automatically fails a random skill test (chosen by the GM) made in the next WIL ÷ 5 minutes. \n\nWith a superior success, you may choose which skill will\nfail the next time it is used (if that skill is not used within the duration, the sleight has no effect) or make the failure a superior failure. This usually manifests as the type of common mistake that even a seasoned professional might make. For example, in combat the target could forget to reload a weapon or alert an ally of a flanking foe. \n\nOut of combat, the target might save the wrong file, forget where they left something, mistake someone for someone else, or leave a security door unlocked.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"D1RzsbFqU7Rm7Umc"}
{"name":"Burst of Confidence","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You instill the target with renewed determination and empowerment.They receive +1 Moxie pool for WIL ÷ 5 minutes. A target may only benefit from one burst of confidence at a time.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"DBIfb8BzpGsi32S2"}
{"name":"Psychic Stab","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You trigger dangerous neurochemical impulses and biofeedback\nin the target’s brain and nervous system. You inflict 2d10 DV, +1d6 per superior success, reduced by mental armor.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"DvbwksDDZSouGhl0"}
{"name":"Sublimal","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You implant a single post-hypnotic suggestion into the target’s mind which they will carry out as if it was their own idea. \n\nImplanted suggestions must be short and simple; the GM may require suggestions be encompassed in a short sentence (for example: “open the airlock” or “hand over the weapon”). Suggestions may include a short trigger condition (“when the alarm goes off, ignore it”). \n\nThe target receives a WIL Check to resist any suggestion that is immediately life threatening (“jump off the bridge”) or that violates their motivations or personal strictures.","active":true,"infection":10,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Hours"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"F1FmFu80kwdOMdpi"}
{"name":"Burst of Clarity","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You refresh the target’s mind, enabling them to see things in a new light. They receive +1 Insight pool for WIL ÷ 5 minutes. A target may only benefit from one burst of clarity at a time.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"FTxXnsHHRW4jYisN"}
{"name":"Aphasia","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You create a temporary stroke-like effect within the target’s brain that disrupts their speech and language centers. \n\nFor WIL ÷ 5 minutes, they are incapable of speaking, communicating, reading, and understanding language.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"Gjd3LPMtDxGNT757"}
{"name":"Sense Infection","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You detect whether the target is infected with a biological nanovirus or nanoplague strain of the exsurgent virus — or if they are an async. \n\nYou know only whether or not the target is infected; superior successes may provide gut feelings about the target’s specific strain and its effects. GM note: under no circumstances should you provide the name of the strain — focus on its nature.","active":true,"infection":2,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"Ix6B1Gdy15bW11iS"}
{"name":"Xeno-Empathy","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You have an intuitive understanding of non-human, non-terrestrial organisms (animal analogues). You can make a SAV Check to acquire insight into the creature’s ecological niche, motivations,needs, and likely behavioral responses (if non-sapient) or mental/emotional state (if sapient).","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"L1QdMzHqpXzmNsWe"}
{"name":"Nightmare","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You bombard the target with horrific images and sensations,\neroding their mental stability. You inflict 2d10 SV to the target, +1d6 per superior success. This is reduced by mental armor.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"LiitKy3XwQRf5Iv1"}
{"name":"Implant Skill","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You impart your expertise and implant it into the target’s mind. The target acquires your chosen existing skill at half value for WIL ÷ 5 hours. \n\nIf the target already has the skill, they use whichever\nvalue is higher. Specialization bonuses also apply. Psi skill may only be implanted if the target has the Psi trait. \n\nRecipients of skills will exercise them with the async’s flair and mannerisms.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Hours"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"LrjPwk8ukNcOdiyX"}
{"name":"Browse Thoughts","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You scan the target’s surface thoughts, gaining a general sense of what is currently running through their mind. Superior successes provide deeper detail. This is not an invasive delve into the target’s mind for specific information like Deep Scan; instead, you simply get a read on what the target is currently thinking.","active":true,"infection":4,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"PBmFCJXJZ6W301Ng"}
{"name":"Spam","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You overload and flood the target’s sensory cortices, spamming them with confusing and distracting sensory input. The target is impaired, suffering –10 to all actions, plus an extra –10 per superior success, for WIL ÷ 5 action turns.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Actions Turns"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"Q14w4z5Ups1R2HyD"}
{"name":"Eco-Empathy","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"With a successful COG Check, you acquire an intuitive understanding of non-sentient, non-terrestrial organisms occupying a producer niche in the local ecosystem (e.g., alien plant and fungus analogues). \n\nThe information you gain is of a general and qualitative\nnature, and doesn’t include data you would normally acquire from chemical or genetic analysis. For example, you could determine if a plant thrives only in riparian zones, if it relies on insect analogs for pollination, or if it produces tubers that are edible to transhumans when cooked.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"QBuTn9cotZva8K6q"}
{"name":"Illusion","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You craft an illusion and inflict it upon the target. The illusion can range from a simple single-sense impression to a completely immersive false reality and can override actual sensory input. \n\nThe illusion cannot directly harm the target, but it can provoke reactions that are dangerous or even fatal (i.e., tricking someone into walking off a roof ). Because the illusion is unsubstantial, it also may not stop or start movement, hold weight, provide protection, etc. \n\nIf the target carefully examines the illusion or physically interacts with it, they receive an INT Check to see through it. Likewise, if the illusion in any way defies reality or inspires common-sense incredulity, or the real world interferes with the illusion (sudden loud noises, walls hidden by the illusion impede movement, etc.), the target gets an INT Check to disbelieve. Targets that succeed in their INT Check will still faintly experience the illusory input, but recognize it as unreal. \n\nNo check is needed if the target has proof the illusion is false. Complex or lengthy illusions are hard to sustain; the GM may call for INT Checks or appropriate skill tests to maintain the constructed facade.\n\nIllusions require intense mental power to sustain. You may not take any complex actions while sustaining this sleight, else the illusion will falter.","active":true,"infection":8,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"T36q4G74ZcQHw3Es"}
{"name":"Alter Effect","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You trigger or ease a neurochemical response within the target, either decreasing or increasing the duration of a drug, chemical, or\ntoxin by half.","active":true,"infection":2,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"T9UW0o5QPDgBNMob"}
{"name":"Superior Kinesics","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You haver finer control over your emotive signals, body language, and micro-expressions and are more capable at interpreting the same in others. +10 to Deceive and Kinesics Tests.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"UOcUTALOraUIX7j8"}
{"name":"Basilisk Stare","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You make eye contact with the target and immobilize them. As long as you keep your gaze locked on them (minor blinking aside), they cannot move, avert their eyes, or undertake any action (including mesh and mental actions). \n\nYou must also limit your movement, though you may move at half your base move and/or take quick physical actions, but you must make a REF Check to keep your eyes locked, and actions requiring a test and visual coordination suffer a\n–30 modifier. Likewise, if the target is attacked, moved, or otherwise jostled, eye contact is lost.\n\nYou may not affect extra targets with this sleight, unless you have more than one set of eyes.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Task","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"UcBKgp8tyYDfi0cp"}
{"name":"Self Control","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your will is tempered and unyielding. +10 to WIL Checks.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"VfQctva0THlx9XIf"}
{"name":"Charisma","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your inhibitions are lowered, social intuition expanded, and\nemotional intelligence augmented. This enhances your ability\nto navigate social situations and process emotional information.\n\nIncrease Moxie pool by 1.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"XFltFZkWYTOTqHQk"}
{"name":"Cloud Memory","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You temporarily disrupt the target’s ability to form long-term memories. The target will retain short-term memories during the duration (WIL ÷ 5 minutes), but will soon (after d6 + 4 action turns) forget anything that occurred while this sleight was in effect.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Minutes"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"XLLIytSWUeg2owEz"}
{"name":"Short Circuit","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You force the target’s synapses to misfire. This functions like a shock attack; the target loses neuromuscular control, falls down, and is incapacitated for 1 action turn (+2 turns per superior success) and stunned for 3 minutes.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"YLUDTH4oT1jE3DJ4"}
{"name":"Downtime","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You slip the target’s mind into a fugue-state regenerative downtime, to repair their psyche. You must sustain this sleight for 4 hours during which you may take no other complex actions. Downtime cannot be concurrent with a long recharge. This process heals 1d6 stress, +1d6 per superior success. Traumas and disorders are unaffected by this sleight. If interrupted, no stress is healed. For all sensory purposes, you and the target are catatonic during downtime, completely oblivious to the outside world. Only severe disturbances or physical shock (such as being wounded or hit by a shock weapon) will bring you or the target out of it. Any target of this sleight other than yourself must make a WIL Check; if they fail, sometime within the next 24 hours they will be subject to one of your influence effects.","active":true,"infection":2,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Task","duration":"Sustained"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"Z3pAxmYa8kQtSAYW"}
{"name":"Inner Spark","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You have an inner well of energy, making it easier to recuperate. You recover +1 pool points during short recharges.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"ZULPDBQnostIXp69"}
{"name":"Empathic Scan","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You sense the target’s emotional state for WIL ÷ 5 action turns. This provides you with a +10 modifier for social skill tests against the target, +10 per superior success. This sleight will not automatically detect deceit, but it will pick up on nervousness, doubt, anxiety, etc. and provide a bonus to Kinesics Tests against Deceive.","active":true,"infection":4,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Actions Turns"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"ZoWuUNGf4EzISOcX"}
{"name":"Qualia","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You have a more intuitive grasp on the world around you. +1 Insight pool.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"bq6KqxA620j7hkU2"}
{"name":"Implant Memory","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You implant a memory of up to an hour’s length inside the\ntarget’s mind. This memory may be completely fabricated, based on your real memories, or a combination of the two. \n\nImplanting real memories is useful for archiving important data with an ally, providing a literal alternate perspective, or simply making a memory dump for the target to peruse. Fake memories are often fuzzy and lacking detail, but bolstering them with real memories makes them more convincing. \n\nAt the GM’s discretion, a fake memory that contradicts the target’s other memories, is drastically out of character, or includes details that inspire skepticism may be identified as false with an INT Check. Particularly traumatic memories may inflict mental stress on the recipient when they are first experienced. Implanted memories do not overwrite real memories.","active":true,"infection":6,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Instant"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"buOMgHgE3RQ8PNrk"}
{"name":"Grok","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You intuitively understand how to use an unfamiliar object, vehicle, or device, no matter how alien, advanced, or bizarre. \n\nYou may make a COG Check to determine how to activate or use it, simply by looking at and handling it. This sleight does not provide any understanding of the principles or technologies involved — you simply grasp how to make it work. This sleight is only effective with unfamiliar devices, it provides no bonus when using devices with which you are familiar.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"dfnpS2hxM3pnpXFr"}
{"name":"Block Sense","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You short-circuit and temporary disable one of the target’s sensory cortices (your choice). For WIL ÷ 5 action turns, the target loses that type of sensory input. The senses that may be negated include sight, hearing, touch, smell, taste, hunger, balance, direction, proprioception, facial recognition, and augmented senses such as electrical sense and radiation sense. Any actions that rely on the impaired sense require a test with a minimum –30 modifier.","active":true,"infection":4,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Actions Turns"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"eUvWFHW3JM2pHCps"}
{"name":"Savant Calculation","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You have an incredible faculty for intuitive mathematics involving complex, chaotic systems. You can calculate your odds when gambling, predict the outcome of stock market upheavals, and guesstimate the rubble distribution pattern from an explosion. \n\nYou can also measure exact distances with a look, solve math problems faster than computers, and tell how many microbots make up a swarmanoid. This talent, however, is not conscious, it is intuitive.\n\nYou do not know the equations you are solving, you simply know the solution. You may make COG Checks to calculate answers to complex mathematical questions.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"eYAKqFQzlKXhCwtq"}
{"name":"Psi Armor","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Your mind’s defenses are solidified. You gain mental armor equal to your WIL ÷ 3 against psi attacks.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"gfpYFi3vWMVvDZPX"}
{"name":"Scramble","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"Scramble helps you to hide from another async using the ego sense sleight. Apply a –30 modifier to the async’s Psi Test.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"iDfcbswa6UG30JNM"}
{"name":"Ego Sense","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You detect the presence and location (rough direction from yourself ) of other sentient and biological life forms (i.e., egos and animals) within Close range. \n\nEach life form makes an opposed test against your roll.\nYou suffer modifiers for size, the same as for ranged attacks. Superior successes provide additional details: approximate size, exact distance, type of creature, etc. If the target moves during the duration (WIL ÷ 5 action turns), you will have a rough idea of their speed and bearing.","active":true,"infection":2,"psiType":"Gamma","actionType":"Complex","duration":"Actions Turns"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/bond.png","effects":[],"_id":"jCSHVYj1iAlzjiZ2"}
{"name":"Enhanced Memory","permission":{"default":0,"4j5oR1x1MdY89nTc":3},"type":"aspect","data":{"description":"You have a perfect memory. Unlike transhumans with hyperthymesia, this is not strictly autobiographical. You can be asked a random date and immediately recall trivial details such as the day of the week it was, what you did that day, what the weather was like, and the exact wording of a paragraph you read. Your memory is always “on” — in fact, you perceive reality and memory much like a\nsplit screen and are often caught in reverie. Enhanced memory has no effect on psychosurgery memory editing.\n\nYou can push this sleight to recall your memories from a sort of third-person point of view, allowing you to make Perceive Tests to notice details you may have previously missed.","active":true,"infection":null,"psiType":"Chi"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/eclipsephase/resources/icons/lotus.png","effects":[],"_id":"lHbyRfRMok19xlSL"}
